      "seed": 655510620,
      "version": 62,
      "versionNonce": 1924321130,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1740517538924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "what happens when a zone goes down\n✅ If You Use FSLogix + Azure Files (ZRS)\n✔ User logs into another VM (manual reassignment needed).\n✔ All data and settings are intact—profile is loaded from Azure Files.\n✔ Minimal disruption, just requires a new VM.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "what happens when a zone goes down\n✅ If You Use FSLogix + Azure Files (ZRS)\n✔ User logs into another VM (manual reassignment needed).\n✔ All data and settings are intact—profile is loaded from Azure Files.\n✔ Minimal disruption, just requires a new VM.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "wd4UStBNghkeCpF5O-KYd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1153.866760253906,
      "y": 4525.140844302707,
      "width": 842.79931640625,
      "height": 175,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "c0NW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1623958884,
      "version": 118,
      "versionNonce": 1647555638,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1740517538924,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "options\n1. Deploy Standby Personal VMs in Another Zone\nPre-provision backup personal session hosts in a different availability zone.\nUse Azure Virtual Desktop PowerShell scripts or automation to reassign users quickly.\n2. backup and restore in another zone-manual\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "options\n1. Deploy Standby Personal VMs in Another Zone\nPre-provision backup personal session hosts in a different availability zone.\nUse Azure Virtual Desktop PowerShell scripts or automation to reassign users quickly.\n2. backup and restore in another zone-manual\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
