      "locked": false,
      "text": "metrics(90 days), near Realtime\nregular collection interval, numeric values\nare stored in a time-series database that's optimized for analyzing time-stamped data.\nTime-stamping makes metrics well suited for alerting and fast detection of issues. \nMetrics can tell you how your system is performing but typically must be combined with logs to \nidentify the root cause of issues.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "metrics(90 days), near Realtime\nregular collection interval, numeric values\nare stored in a time-series database that's optimized for analyzing time-stamped data.\nTime-stamping makes metrics well suited for alerting and fast detection of issues. \nMetrics can tell you how your system is performing but typically must be combined with logs to \nidentify the root cause of issues.",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
